# RDX Code Standards (src/)

## Structure

- New UI: `src/components/rdx/` only
- New copy/data: `src/content/rdx/` only
- Server Components default; `"use client"` only for forms/interactivity

## Style

- Use tokens from `src/styles/rdx/tokens.css`
- No Fiverr green on rdx components
- No `Enhanced*`, `*V2`, `*New` file names
- Max ~150 lines/page — extract sections

## Quality

- No `console.log` in shipped code
- No commented-out legacy blocks left behind
- No `any` without comment
- Reuse existing `Button`/`Card` before cloning

## Copy

Use `docs/RDX_Content_Copy_Bank.md`. Never invent stats.

Full standards: `docs/RDX_Implementation_Standards.md`
